  "Description": {
    "English": "A writhing cocoon, the spawning sac of a grub of the <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">vile brood</span>.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has <span class=\"name name-special\">anomalous</span> genetic material, an <span class=\"name name-fuel\">unstable</span> binding of several independent strands.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "不停扭动的虫茧，负责为<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">邪恶虫群</span>生成幼虫。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，其中的生物拥有着<span class=\"name name-special\">异常</span>的基因材料，并且由多条独立的基因链以<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不稳定</span>的方式结合而成。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "蠕動的繭，這是<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">邪惡巢穴</span>的幼蟲繁殖卵囊。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，其中具有<span class=\"name name-special\">異常</span>的基因材料，為若干獨立物種的<span class=\"name name-fuel\">不穩定</span>結合。"
  },
